short_description: Happy Teeth are ARTISEN MADE in the USA starting with Himalayan Cheese and using innovative & traditional Himalayan techniques that utilize all-natural ingredients, no preservatives, no binding agents.

product_description: Happy Teeth are our great tasting dental chew. With its loofah like texture, Happy Teeth cleans teeth, fights against plaque and tarter build-up and freshens breath. The best part, there is no medicinal smell or taste; just a great tasting treat! Happy Teeth is good for dogs of all ages and sizes; from puppies to seniors. Happy Teeth are lactose, grain and gluten free and is easily digestible. These all-natural dental chews are available in three delectable flavors your dog will enjoy; cheese, cheese with real peanut butter and cheese with real bacon. It’s important to choose a chew that matches your dog’s chewing rate, age and habits. Check out our Chewmeter to help you make the best choice for your dog. You can find the Chewmeter on the back of all our packaging. Advice for use Give as reward or treat Supervise pets when giving them any treat Best for dogs over 12 weeks old Not for human consumption Happy Teeth should be kept in a cool and dry place (do not refrigerate) Wash hands after handling products with dog drool Remove treat if potential hazard presents itself.
